(226, 'Bugis Thai Isaan Kitchen', 'Thai', '$', 'Bugis', '4.3', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562565652-a0d8f0c59eb4?w=600&q=80', 'Fiery Isaan cooking from Northeastern Thailand. The laab moo is explosively good.'),
