(229, 'Toa Payoh Peranakan Kitchen', 'Local', '$$', 'Toa Payoh', '4.5', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908176997-125f25cc6f3d?w=600&q=80', 'Heartland Peranakan with genuine family recipes. The sambal udang is unforgettable.'),
